 |_____\__,_/__/\__|   \__/\__/\___/_| \__,_/__/  @{b}from Glen Martin@{ub}

 Everything by me  (doors, docs, etc) are copyrighted (c) GREMLiNS MAXsWARE
 Use this door at your own risk, it's provided as is...  So don't blame me!

 The Door  works  perfectly, and no limitations.  Selecting  the  Info Menu
 displays the info file,  and shows a prompt to what BBS the  Door is owned
 by, and  nothing more.  Advicing  me you want to register means  you get a
 personal copy which shows your BBS, so no big deal.

 I'll be in UK within the year!  It'll happen... unless I die! ;-)

@endnode
